{"tid":785774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞運孫楊游泳奪金　頒獎後升中國國旗期間金屬支架突倒下　","createTime":"2018-08-19T12:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T11:30:33.000Z","uid":41404,"like":613,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"e24604a4f1bc9ce5bd95c5709a8125b09fe58971","tid":785774,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1413310_1_20180819203841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1413310_1_20180819203841.jpg&h=64049494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大會在播放國歌及升國旗時，掛著旗幟的金屬支架突然倒下。（馮卓垣攝）<br />\n<br />\n亞運游泳比賽，中國泳手孫楊在男子200米自由泳奪得金牌。大會頒發獎牌後，播放國歌及升國旗時，掛著旗幟的金屬支架突然倒下，大會再次播放國歌及升國旗。<br />\n<br />\n大會之後頒發女子200米背泳獎牌時，沒有再使用金屬支架升旗，只是安排三名人員手持三面旗幟，這個項目由中國的劉雅欣奪得金牌。<br />\n<br />\n另外，港隊的黃筠陶在女子200米背泳決賽得第六，林凱喬在女子1500米自由泳決賽排名第七，楊珍美就在女子100米蛙泳決賽以第六名完成。"},{"pid":"80e42b149ec701ab5a57f439cc8c9b6dd9c5c139","tid":785774,"uid":29942,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766b638f7b1e815a49653fe0cee8995f2a01eb0f","tid":785774,"uid":15984,"like":228,"dislike":6,"score":222,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:59:23.000Z","msg":"陳浩天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddf29ee5f99026590b0e64aabfc0ef619cfb9ae","tid":785774,"uid":125357,"like":166,"dislike":1,"score":165,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"天㓕中共"},{"pid":"d9000d69709594c5790f3c8cf37f7e254e816ab6","tid":785774,"uid":8858,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"c4a5f083fad636f34bb56c